    "import os, sys\n",
    "os.environ[\"TILE_FWK_DEVICE_ID\"] = \"0\"\n",
    "import pypto\n",
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch_npu\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "\n",
    "device_id = int(os.environ[\"TILE_FWK_DEVICE_ID\"])\n",
    "torch.npu.set_device(device_id)\n",
    "device = f\"npu:{device_id}\"\n",
    "mode = pypto.RunMode.NPU"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f45c7446-dd57-4252-b66d-a273cd034dca",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 练习 1\n",
    "证明一个矩阵 $A$ 的转置的转置是 $A$，即 $(A^\\top)^\\top = A$。\n",
    "\n",
    "**解答：**\n",
    "\n",
    "假设存在 $A^\\top = B$, $B^\\top = C$，根据矩阵转置的定义，可得：  \n",
    "$b_{ij} = a_{ji}$，$c_{ij} = b_{ji}$\n",
    "\n",
    "易知：  \n",
    "$c_{ij} = b_{ji} = a_{ij}$\n",
    "\n",
    "则：  \n",
    "$c_{ij} = a_{ij}$\n",
    "\n",
    "根据矩阵定义，可得：  \n",
    "$C = A = B^\\top = (A^\\top)^\\top$\n",
    "\n",
    "以下使用 `torch` 编程进行验证："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 15,
   "id": "72d41c7f-c842-4ad6-b132-dcca4dd656d1",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "tensor([[True, True, True, True],\n",
       "        [True, True, True, True],\n",
       "        [True, True, True, True],\n",
       "        [True, True, True, True],\n",
       "        [True, True, True, True]])"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 15,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "A = torch.arange(20).reshape(5, 4)\n",
    "A.T.T == A"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "7714e174-e9f2-4091-80e8-9d85861a9b23",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "使用 `PyPTO` 编程进行验证:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cc473190-c0f0-473a-9c7b-971046f05977",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "@pypto.frontend.jit(runtime_options={\"run_mode\": mode})\n",
    "def practice01_kernel(\n",
    "    out: pypto.Tensor([], pypto.DT_BOOL),\n",
    "):\n",
    "    pypto.set_vec_tile_shapes(5, 8)\n",
    "    A = pypto.arange(20.0).reshape([5, 4])\n",
    "    out.move(pypto.eq(A, A.transpose(0, 1).transpose(0, 1)))\n",
    "\n",
    "out = torch.zeros((5, 4), dtype=torch.bool, device=device)\n",
    "practice01_kernel(out)\n",
    "out"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f5e5a3bf-9e53-4489-9f3d-7612aef1c8bd",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 练习 2\n",
    "给出两个矩阵 $A$ 和 $B$，证明“它们转置的和”等于“它们和的转置”，即 $A^\\top + B^\\top = (A + B)^\\top$。\n",
    "\n",
    "**解答：**\n",
    "\n",
    "假设 $C = A + B$，根据矩阵运算的定义可得：  \n",
    "$c_{ij} = a_{ij} + b_{ij}$\n",
    "\n",
    "对矩阵 $C$ 进行转置，将 $i,j$ 进行互换，可得：  \n",
    "$c_{ij} = a_{ji} + b_{ji}$\n",
    "\n",
    "根据矩阵定义，可得：  \n",
    "$C^\\top = A^\\top + B^\\top = (A + B)^\\top$\n",
    "\n",
    "以下使用 `torch` 编程进行验证："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 16,
   "id": "9d23ba30-e3fe-42d4-98a9-79a16c0c0862",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "tensor([[True, True, True, True],\n",
       "        [True, True, True, True],\n",
       "        [True, True, True, True],\n",
       "        [True, True, True, True]])"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 16,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "A = torch.rand(4, 4)\n",
    "B = torch.rand(4, 4)\n",
    "A.T + B.T == (A + B).T"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "a6b1c0e3-9de2-406d-8d63-c1cd3c417017",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "使用 `PyPTO` 编程进行验证:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 17,
   "id": "2d9fb9a1-dd60-4811-9b06-8b6ea8aa8775",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "tensor([[True, True, True, True],\n",
       "        [True, True, True, True],\n",
       "        [True, True, True, True],\n",
       "        [True, True, True, True]], device='npu:0')"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 17,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "@pypto.frontend.jit(runtime_options={\"run_mode\": mode})\n",
    "def practice02_kernel(\n",
    "    a: pypto.Tensor([], pypto.DT_FP32),\n",
    "    b: pypto.Tensor([], pypto.DT_FP32),\n",
    "    out: pypto.Tensor([], pypto.DT_BOOL),\n",
    "):\n",
    "    pypto.set_vec_tile_shapes(5, 8)\n",
    "    out.move(pypto.eq(a.transpose(0, 1) + b.transpose(0, 1), (a + b).transpose(0, 1)))\n",
    "    \n",
    "A = torch.rand(4, 4, dtype=torch.float32, device=device)\n",
    "B = torch.rand(4, 4, dtype=torch.float32, device=device)\n",
    "out = torch.zeros((4, 4), dtype=torch.bool, device=device)\n",
    "practice02_kernel(A, B, out)\n",
    "out"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "8b462637-7a37-4ff4-abec-f088c7d4be4f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 练习 3\n",
    "给定任意方阵 $A$，$A + A^\\top$ 总是对称的吗？为什么？\n",
    "\n",
    "**解答：**\n",
    "\n",
    "假设 $B = A + A^\\top$，根据矩阵运算的定义可得：  \n",
    "$b_{ij} = a_{ij} + a_{ji}$\n",
    "\n",
    "对矩阵 $B$ 进行转置，将 $i,j$ 进行互换，可得：  \n",
    "$b_{ji} = a_{ji} + a_{ij}$\n",
    "\n",
    "根据矩阵定义，可得：  \n",
    "$B^\\top = A^\\top + A = (A + A^\\top)$\n",
    "\n",
    "所以，根据对称矩阵的定义，给定任意方阵 $A$，$A + A^\\top$ 是对称矩阵。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d2df3f08-e0fb-4b64-bdd0-7cf878bfa054",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 练习 4\n",
    "本节中定义了形状 $(2, 3, 4)$ 的张量 `X`。`len(X)` 的输出结果是什么？\n",
    "\n",
    "**解答：** 2\n",
    "\n",
    "以下使用 `torch` 编程进行验证："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 18,
   "id": "d3552e50-0b64-482b-8379-ef4a8c3ce115",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "2"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 18,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "X = torch.arange(24).reshape(2, 3, 4)\n",
    "len(X)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "4c9e9e3c-e786-4e02-bb00-79a35043b6b7",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "在 [2.3 节](../02.03_linear_algebra.ipynb) 中，我们提到：`PyPTO` 的 `Tensor` 并未提供 `len()` 支持。作为替代，可以通过 `.shape` 属性获取符号化的维度信息。\n",
    " \n",
    "但在使用 `.shape` 替代 `len()` 时，需注意**语义差异**：\n",
    " \n",
    "| 方法 | 语义 | 返回类型 |\n",
    "|------|------|----------|\n",
    "| `len(X)` | 张量沿 **轴 0** 的长度 | `int` |\n",
    "| `X.shape` | 张量的**整体形状**（各维度大小构成的列表） | `List[SymInt]` |\n",
    " \n",
    "因此，若要用 `PyPTO` 模拟 `torch` 中 `len()` 的行为，应取 `.shape` 的第 0 个元素：\n",
    " "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 19,
   "id": "e4e8b4fa-7f06-4c73-b388-04fdb87bcb65",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "[JIT] X.shape[0] = 2\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "@pypto.frontend.jit(runtime_options={\"run_mode\": pypto.RunMode.NPU})\n",
    "def test04_kernel(\n",
    "    out: pypto.Tensor([2, 3, 4], pypto.DT_FP32), \n",
    "):\n",
    "    pypto.set_vec_tile_shapes(2, 3, 8)\n",
    "    X = pypto.arange(24).reshape([2, 3, 4])\n",
    "    print(f\"[JIT] X.shape[0] = {X.shape[0]}\")\n",
    "    out.move(X)\n",
    " \n",
    "out = torch.zeros(2, 3, 4, device=device)\n",
    "test04_kernel(out)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "a84783f0-1aa4-4005-a0e1-862a7a5806bb",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
