   "source": [
    "## 练习 6\n",
    "运行 `A / A.sum(axis=1)`，看看会发生什么。请分析一下原因？\n",
    "\n",
    "**解答：**\n",
    "\n",
    "直接运行会报错，因为 `A.sum(axis=1)` 得到的形状与 `A` 不兼容，无法广播。正确做法是加上 `keepdims=True`。\n",
    "以下使用 `torch` 编程进行验证:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 23,
   "id": "6c743200-33b6-44ba-a378-7dd6ba0a3794",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "The size of tensor a (4) must match the size of tensor b (5) at non-singleton dimension 1\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# 错误做法\n",
    "A = torch.arange(20).reshape(5, 4)\n",
    "try:\n",
    "    A / A.sum(axis=1)\n",
    "except Exception as e:\n",
    "    print(e)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 24,
   "id": "5c59907e-d58e-49a9-8e12-e1f2d03fa55b",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "tensor([[0.0000, 0.1667, 0.3333, 0.5000],\n",
       "        [0.1818, 0.2273, 0.2727, 0.3182],\n",
       "        [0.2105, 0.2368, 0.2632, 0.2895],\n",
       "        [0.2222, 0.2407, 0.2593, 0.2778],\n",
       "        [0.2286, 0.2429, 0.2571, 0.2714]])"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 24,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# 正确做法\n",
    "A / A.sum(axis=1, keepdims=True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "5b44253c-d55e-4851-af20-e5f72cdf2142",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "使用 `PyPTO` 编程进行验证:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 25,
   "id": "f9bb6ab1-a8ff-4a09-bc9e-a3ec77e26c85",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "tensor([[0.0000, 0.1667, 0.3333, 0.5000],\n",
       "        [0.1818, 0.2273, 0.2727, 0.3182],\n",
       "        [0.2105, 0.2368, 0.2632, 0.2895],\n",
       "        [0.2222, 0.2407, 0.2593, 0.2778],\n",
       "        [0.2286, 0.2429, 0.2571, 0.2714]], device='npu:0')"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 25,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "@pypto.frontend.jit(runtime_options={\"run_mode\": mode})\n",
    "def practice06_kernel(\n",
    "    a: pypto.Tensor([], pypto.DT_FP32),\n",
    "    out: pypto.Tensor([], pypto.DT_FP32),\n",
    "):\n",
    "    pypto.set_vec_tile_shapes(5, 8)\n",
    "    out.move(pypto.div(a, a.sum(dim=1, keepdim=True)))\n",
    "    \n",
    "A = torch.arange(20.0, dtype=torch.float32, device=device).reshape(5, 4)\n",
    "out = torch.zeros((5, 4), dtype=torch.float32, device=device)\n",
    "practice06_kernel(A, out)\n",
    "out"
   ]
  },
